# Changamire Dombo (1695–1720)
# Changamire Zharare ()
# Changamire Negamo (–1710)
# Chirisamuru (–1788)
# Changamire Dhafa(–1824)
# Changamire Baswi ()
# Changamire Chirisamuru II (–1836)
# Changamire Tohwechipi Zharare (1838–1866)

